snippet.title: Blazing Beaks | Multiplayer mayhem! | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Aye aye lads, did you know that you can play Blazing Beaks in co-op or even challenge your friends in versus mode?
Those two parrots know for sure! Time for you to try it. 😎
Get more info about the game here 
⏩ http://bit.ly/BlazingBeakseShop

Here's the website of the original footage's author 
⏩ http://quatro.studio/
